; Regression test for issue #603: print ignores @tag ... @end tag (BZ#603)
; https://github.com/ledger/ledger/issues/603
;
; When 'apply tag' is used to apply metadata tags to a group of transactions,
; the 'print' command should include those tags in the output. Currently, print
; outputs the transactions without any tag metadata, so the tag information is
; lost if the output is used as a journal file.

apply tag Category: Testing

2024/01/01 Test Transaction
    Expenses:Food    $10.00
    Assets:Cash

end apply tag

test print
2024/01/01 Test Transaction
    Expenses:Food                             $10.00
    Assets:Cash
end test
